s1: Login Slack

s2: Create an App (https://api.slack.com/apps) from scratch
App Name: Jenkins
Workspace: DevOps
Click Create App.

Step 3: Add OAuth Scopes

On the left menu, go to:

OAuth & Permissions

Under Bot Token Scopes, add these scopes:

chat:write
chat:write.public
files:write
channels:read
groups:read
Step 4: Install the App

Scroll to the top of the same page and click:

Install to Workspace

Approve the permissions.

Step 5: Copy the Bot Token

After installation you'll see:

Bot User OAuth Token: "token"

This xoxb-... token is what Jenkins uses.

Step 6: Add the Token in Jenkins

Go to:

Manage Jenkins
    ↓
Credentials
    ↓
Global
    ↓
Add Credentials

Choose:

Kind:
Secret text

Secret:

xoxb-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

ID:

slack-token
Step 7: Configure the Slack Plugin

Go to:

Manage Jenkins
    ↓
Configure System
    ↓
Slack

Configure:

Workspace Name:
DevOps

Credential:
slack-token

Default Channel:
#all-devops

Click Test Connection.




Pipeline:
pipeline {
    agent any

    stages {

        stage('Build') {
            steps {
                echo "Building application..."
            }
        }

        stage('Test') {
            steps {
                echo "Running tests..."
            }
        }
    }

    post {
        success {
            slackSend(
                channel: '#all-devops',
                color: 'good',
                message: """✅ *Build Successful*
*Job:* ${env.JOB_NAME}
*Build:* #${env.BUILD_NUMBER}
*Branch:* ${env.BRANCH_NAME}
*URL:* ${env.BUILD_URL}"""
            )
        }

        failure {
            slackSend(
                channel: '#all-devops',
                color: 'danger',
                message: """❌ *Build Failed*
*Job:* ${env.JOB_NAME}
*Build:* #${env.BUILD_NUMBER}
*URL:* ${env.BUILD_URL}"""
            )
        }

        unstable {
            slackSend(
                channel: '#all-devops',
                color: 'warning',
                message: "⚠️ ${env.JOB_NAME} #${env.BUILD_NUMBER} is UNSTABLE.\n${env.BUILD_URL}"
            )
        }
    }
}
